#### D. vm.ts — builtin 호출 시 capability 집행

BUILTIN_REQUIRED_CAPABILITIES Map을 VM에도 두고, builtin 호출 직전에 현재 프레임의 capabilities를 검사:

```typescript
private readonly BUILTIN_REQUIRED_CAPABILITIES = new Map([
  ["file_read", "read_file"],   // 주의: stdlib 실제 이름 file_read (언더스코어)
  ["file_write", "write_file"],
  ["http_get", "network"],
  ["http_request", "network"],
  ["process_spawn", "spawn_process"],
  ["eval", "execute_code"],
])

private checkBuiltinCapability(builtinName: string) {
  const required = this.BUILTIN_REQUIRED_CAPABILITIES.get(builtinName)
  if (!required) return  // 안전한 builtin은 통과

  const currentCaps = this.getCurrentCapabilities()
  const hasCapability = currentCaps.some(c => c.cap === required)

  if (!hasCapability) {
    this.runtimeError(
      `[CapabilityError] '${builtinName}' requires capability '${required}', ` +
      `but current function does not declare it`
    )
  }
}

private getCurrentCapabilities(): Array<{cap: string; arg?: string}> {
  if (this.frames.length === 0) return []
  return this.frames[this.frames.length - 1].capabilities
}
```

#### E. vm.ts — path/host 런타임 검증 (선택적, 심화)

정적 검사에서 `capabilityCovers()` 로직을 VM에도 이식하여 런타임에 경로 인자를 실제 파일 경로와 비교:

```typescript
private checkFileCapability(builtinName: string, actualPath: string) {
  const kind = builtinName.startsWith("file_read") ? "read_file" : "write_file"
  const caps = this.getCurrentCapabilities().filter(c => c.cap === kind)
  if (caps.length === 0) this.runtimeError(`Missing capability: ${kind}`)

  const allowed = caps.some(c => !c.arg || this.pathIsUnder(actualPath, c.arg))
  if (!allowed) this.runtimeError(
    `[CapabilityError] Access to '${actualPath}' denied (allowed: ${caps.map(c => c.arg).join(", ")})`
  )
}
```

